Introduction

Gunwoo (also known as T28) is a South Korean singer, rapper and dancer under Roots Entertainment. He is a former member of the boy group TFN. He later made his solo debut on March 10, 2025 with the digital single "Shot".

He is also known for being a contestant on the reality survival show Starlight Boys.
